{
  "stem": "4967.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We arrived in Kaufering [SPEAKING GERMAN], working camp number one, Dachau.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was a new camp, a working camp, which they brought the people there to work for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They actually were building an airplane factory Messerschmitt in the later stage of the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We disembarked of these trains.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And as we disembarked the train, we had to go through the gate.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "You had to take off your civilian clothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They gave you striped clothing, blue and white stripes, no underwear, and they gave you wood shoes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "The sole was thick wood sole and material, like a military [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "It's a hard material and shoelaces if you have any.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "For me, they didn't have my size.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And I was lucky remained with my [GERMAN], my boots, which are made in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I paid 5,000 mark, German marks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And with this, I arrived in Dachau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "In these shoes, [GERMAN], I had Russian currency.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And I had three or four [? 10 ?] Russian ruble gold coins, I think three or four.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Before-- before we changed the clothing, they checked the mens, examined them, whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "They looked for gold, for jewelry, diamonds, and this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Anyway, I got dressed in my blue and white strip, gray stripe.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And I [? went in ?] my [GERMAN], my long boots.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "But I put my trouser not inside the boots, outside so the Germans couldn't see if I got boots.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And with these boots, I went through all the year in this concentration camp, Dachau [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "They asked us in our underwears our own barracks made out of masonite, 10 people to each barrack.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And as you came in, we got a number.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And we were registered by Jewish clerks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "They were mostly Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
